{"tid":869270,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【iReserve 都唔洗開】iPhone XR 堅任撳 ！！！！！！！","createTime":"2018-10-20T08:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T16:08:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ff61be5df7f6814d37b76ba57feb41b06b9db6","tid":869270,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T08:14:51.000Z","msg":"iPhone XS 跟 XS Max 貨源充足，讓用家對今日開放預售的 iPhone XR 貨量亦同樣樂觀。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/editor/news2016/20181019_news_xrbuy_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews2016%2F20181019_news_xrbuy_01.jpg&h=2dad6240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n果然在 15：01 開售後，所有色款的 iPhone XR 都可以經 AOS訂購，或經 App 版預約功能、在下週五 10 月 26 日正式發售日，到指定 Apple Store 取貨；至於在推出 iPhone XS/XS Max 時有開放的 Web 版iReserve 頁面，這次就索性不啟動（上圖），直接讓用家往 Apple Store 頁面訂購。<br />\n<br />\n雖然 iPhone XR 貨源充足，不過最大容量的 256GB 款式，就基本全面缺貨，未知是否因月前 XS／XS Max 開售時，最高容量的 512GB 機款回收價較高關係，抑或是貨源不多亦未可知。<br />\n<br />\n 今次 iPhone XR 開放預約時，又輪到《Apple Store》比 Safari 網頁較快，在 15：03 時，Web 版網頁仍在「差不多了」等候頁時，《Apple Store》版已可成功登入及挑選 iPhone XR。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/editor/news2016/20181019_news_xrbuy_s01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews2016%2F20181019_news_xrbuy_s01.jpg&h=6eb32348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 15：03 分已可進入《Apple Store》App 挑選 iPhone XR<br />\n <br />\n點擊「型號 &gt; 選擇 iPhone XR」頁面上方「立即預約購買」連結，就可進入 App 版的 iReserve 分頁，當時各色款的 64GB 跟 128GB 容量版本都有現貨提供，試訂 128GB 款 iPhone XR 流暢無難度，3 分鐘完成整個預購程序。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/editor/news2016/20181019_news_xrbuy_s03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews2016%2F20181019_news_xrbuy_s03.jpg&h=2c962435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　<br />\n▲ 各色款 iPhone XR 都可選在 Apple Store 各大分店預約提取<br />\n <br />\n相比 64GB 跟 128GB 容量款式，256GB 版本 iPhone XR 就基本全線缺貨，由珊瑚、藍色等新色，到傳統黑白色款，iReserve 取機都標示「無供應」。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/editor/news2016/20181019_news_xrbuy_s06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews2016%2F20181019_news_xrbuy_s06.jpg&h=64762a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　<br />\n▲ 相比 256GB 容量 iPhone XR 就全線缺貨<br />\n <br />\n於 16：00 左右登入《Apple Store》，各色款的 64GB 、128GB 容量版本 iPhone XR，仍可在各大 Apple Store 中選擇預約提取，似乎代表貨源相當充足，用家們可放心挑選不怕炒機潮。"},{"pid":"78d3f53b03741368bfe1e829c630cd055d40c94a","tid":869270,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T08:15:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ringhk.com/news/ireserve-都唔開-iphone-xr-堅任撳-除左\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Fnews%2Fireserve-%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E9%96%8B-iphone-xr-%E5%A0%85%E4%BB%BB%E6%92%B3-%E9%99%A4%E5%B7%A6&d=CUqz8Jvto69YGFgxZhJLbgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e27d86bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ringhk.com/news/ireserve-都唔開-iphone-xr-堅任撳-除左</a>"},{"pid":"302156ede0d547ce111e4cc907924bad67c718c8","tid":869270,"uid":151333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"全力進攻256, 借財仔一球野，呢鋪仰唔撚上樓dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e07762499211dc6c84a40cca6618928386a9d5","tid":869270,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e034ffd8a03214913e592efe786f29a863c932","tid":869270,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"302156ede0d547ce111e4cc907924bad67c718c8","tid":869270,"uid":151333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"全力進攻256, 借財仔一球野，呢鋪仰唔撚上樓dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:05:12.000Z","msg":"貨源充足喎清"},{"pid":"6c152ee5bd850415fa6d02090105048a5623cabc","tid":869270,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,